metadata.name: Deliverance
metadata.description:
Women are the gems of this world, but in this world women are constantly fighting a battle for their rights to their bodies and the decisions they can make to their own physical body. This can lead to many deaths in women, many mental health issues and many more. 

Nature has a plan to restore balance...only time will tell. Women will rise from the bottom and become fierce once more.

To All women out there..stay fierce, stay strong..you are the gems of the physical world.
